mixin Faq()
    section.faq.container
        h2.title Frequently asked questions

        div.faq-item
            p.question Do I need to download anything to play Funtower?
            p.answer No, Funtower is fully browser-based. Simply visit our website and start playing right away—no downloads or installations needed.

        div.faq-item
            p.question Is Funtower free to play?
            p.answer Yes, Funtower is completely free. You can jump right into the game and start playing without any cost.

        div.faq-item
            p.question Can I play Funtower on my phone or tablet?
            p.answer Absolutely! Funtower is optimized for both desktop and mobile devices, so you can enjoy the game on the go, wherever you are.

        div.faq-item
            p.question How do I play Funtower?
            p.answer The goal of Funtower is to climb as high as possible while avoiding obstacles. Quick thinking and strategy will help you conquer new levels and achieve a high score!

        div.faq-item
            p.question Who can I contact if I have questions or feedback about Funtower?
            p.answer If you have any questions or want to share feedback, just use the contact form at the bottom of the page. The Funtower team is always eager to hear from players!

        div.faq-item
            p.question Can I play Funtower on mobile devices?
            p.answer Yes, Funtower is fully optimized for mobile browsers. Open the game on your smartphone or tablet, and start playing instantly—no downloads required!

        div.faq-item
            p.question Do I need to create an account to play Funtower?
            p.answer No, creating an account is not necessary. Simply visit Funtower's website, start the game, and enjoy the action right away.

        div.faq-item
            p.question Is Funtower free to play?
            p.answer Absolutely! Funtower is free to play. Jump right in and enjoy a fun and exciting game without any hidden costs.

        div.faq-item
            p.question How can I improve my Funtower score?
            p.answer Focus on timing your moves carefully and adapting to new challenges. The more you practice, the better you’ll become at climbing higher and avoiding obstacles.

        div.faq-item
            p.question The game isn’t loading properly. What should I do?
            p.answer Try refreshing the page first. If the issue persists, clear your browser cache or switch to a different browser. If you need further assistance, feel free to contact us via the form at the bottom of the page.

        div.faq-item
            p.question What happens if I fail in Funtower?
            p.answer If you fail, the game ends, and you’ll need to start over. But don’t worry—each new attempt brings fresh excitement, and you’ll keep improving with each play!
